d\ninsight on the strong-field laser-atom interaction mechanism, while\nestablishing the era of phase selective interaction studies. Furthermore, it\npaves the way for substantial enhancement of the spectral and temporal\nprecision of measurements by in-situ controlling the phase distribution of the\nemitted radiation and/or spatially selecting the EUV-radiation-atom interaction\nproducts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Jul 2013 09:19:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 31 Jul 2013 08:55:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
